{"lemma":"رَثّاتٌ","slug":"رَثّاتٌ","root":"ر.ث.ث","root_slug":"ر-ث-ث","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-ث-ث","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":0},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n14735","n14738"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%AB%D9%91%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n14735","headword_ar":"رَثَّ","root":"rv","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, M, &c.,) sec. pers. ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ravavota","text_ar":"رَثَثْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ravivota","text_ar":"رَثِثْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ravuvota","text_ar":"رَثُثْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, K) and"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M) and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,) the last being of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rav~a","text_ar":"رَثَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the class of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaruba","text_ar":"قَرُبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ravaAvapN","text_ar":"رَثَاثَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, Mgh, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruvuwvapN","text_ar":"رُثُوثَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, Msb, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Arv~","text_ar":"ارثّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, M, Msb, K;) both authorized by AZ; the latter at first disallowed by As, but afterwards allowed by him; (M;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, old, and worn out;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, A, Mgh, Msb;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mean,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bad;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M;) namely, a garment, (T, S, M, A, Mgh,) and a rope, (S, M, A,) or other thing, (S, Msb,) i. e. anything, but mostly said of what is worn as clothing, or spread as furniture: (M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, threadbare, shabby,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mean."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) said of a man, it has for its aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yarav~u","text_ar":"يَرَثُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ravaAvapN","text_ar":"رَثَاثَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ravaAvapu Alhayoy^api","text_ar":"رَثَاثَةُ الهَيْيَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An old, worn-out, state of garb"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"apparel;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a bad condition."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) And you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiy hayoy^atihi ravaAvapN","text_ar":"فِي هَيْيَتِهِ رَثَاثَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In his garb,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"apparel, is threadbareness, shabbiness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"meanness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rav~ato hayoy^apu Al$~axoSi","text_ar":"رَثَّتْ هَيْيَةُ الشَّخْصِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Arv~t","text_ar":"ارثّت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The aspect,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition, of the person was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, weak,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vile, mean, paltry,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"despicable."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rav~a Alr~ajulu","text_ar":"رَثَّ الرَّجُلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The man was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, old, and worn out;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weak,"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1030},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rav~N","text_ar":"رَثٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  [And hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY h`*aA Alxabari ravaAvapN","text_ar":"فِى هٰذَا الخَبَرِ رَثَاثَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In this information, announcement, piece of news,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"narration, is unsoundness, invalidity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"incorrectness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiyhi rakaAkapN","text_ar":"فِيهِ رَكَاكَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","T","S","M","K","TA","A","Mgh"]},{"entry_id":"n14738","headword_ar":"رَثٌّ","root":"rv","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Old, and worn out;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, A, Mgh, Msb, K;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mean,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bad;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raviyvN","text_ar":"رَثِيثٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same, (M, A, K,) as does also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arav~u","text_ar":"اَرَثُّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riv~apN","text_ar":"رِثَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, TA: [but this last is app. a subst, as it is said to be in another place in the M and in the TA, meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing that is old, and worn out;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.:]) applied to a garment, (T, M, A, Mgh,) and a rope, (A,) or a thing (S, M, Msb) of any kind, but mostly to what is worn as clothing, or spread as furniture: (M:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rav~N","text_ar":"رَثٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rivaAvN","text_ar":"رِثَاثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, M, Msb.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hayoy^apN rav~apN","text_ar":"هَيْيَةٌ رَثَّةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An old, worn-out, state of garb"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"apparel; such as is in bad condition."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rav~u Alhayoy^api","text_ar":"رَثُّ الهَيْيَةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man whose garb,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"apparel, is old, and worn out;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, * M;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"threadbare, shabby,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mean."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) This last phrase is [also] tropical [as meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man whose aspect,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition, is weak,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vile, mean, paltry,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"despicable:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see 1, last sentence but two]. (A.) And one says also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN rav~N","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ رَثٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man old, and worn out;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weak,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (T.) ―         -b2-  And [hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kalaAmN rav~N","text_ar":"كَلَامٌ رَثٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Meagre, unsubstantial,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flimsy, speech"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"language."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b3-  See also what next follows."}],"source_refs":["M","A","K","T","Mgh","S","Msb"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}